Before starting this game, you must have the AMOS.library in LIBS:



This game is based on the Yeti game I have seen on Thomson TO8 computers

To end a level, you must collect ALL THE FRUITS, and go near the girl.

You can pause the game with the key 'P'.
You can escape the game with 'ESC' and return to the workbench.
You can say : 'nothing new' , but again, too much games don't have these 
features...

This game has been done with AmosPro. AMAL is nice, but now, for
new developpement, you should think to the Blitz Basic, I think, as
I have done...



